<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Spring]]></title><description><![CDATA[Level up your Java code and explore what Spring can do for you.]]></description><link>https://spring.io</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 01:05:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[Spring AI 2.0.0-M4, 1.1.4 and 1.0.5 are available now]]></title><link>https://spring.io/blog/2026/03/26/spring-ai-2-0-0-M4-and-1-1-4-and-1-0-5-available</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://spring.io/blog/2026/03/26/spring-ai-2-0-0-M4-and-1-1-4-and-1-0-5-available</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ilayaperumalg]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;On behalf of the Spring AI engineering team and everyone who has contributed, I&apos;m happy to announce that Spring AI &lt;code&gt;1.0.5&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;1.1.4&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;2.0.0-M4&lt;/code&gt; have been released and are now available from Maven Central.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These releases deliver important improvements, stability enhancements, and bug fixes across multiple release streams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;release-summary&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#release-summary&quot; aria-label=&quot;release summary permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Release Summary&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These releases include a combined total of &lt;strong&gt;51 improvements, bug fixes, and documentation updates&lt;/strong&gt;. See individual release notes: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v1.0.5&quot;&gt;1.0.5&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v1.1.4&quot;&gt;1.1.4&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v2.0.0-M4&quot;&gt;2.0.0-M4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The focus of these releases includes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improvements&lt;/strong&gt;: 19 enhancements across all releases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stability&lt;/strong&gt;: 29 bug fixes addressing community-reported issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt;: 3 dependency upgrades for enhanced security and fixes for &lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/security/cve-2026-22738&quot;&gt;CVE-2026-22738&lt;/a&gt; , &lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/security/cve-2026-22742&quot;&gt;CVE-2026-22742&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/security/cve-2026-22743&quot;&gt;CVE-2026-22743&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/security/cve-2026-22744&quot;&gt;CVE-2026-22744&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks to all those who have contributed with issue reports and pull requests.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;version-specific-highlights&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#version-specific-highlights&quot; aria-label=&quot;version specific highlights permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Version-Specific Highlights&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;spring-ai-105&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#spring-ai-105&quot; aria-label=&quot;spring ai 105 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Spring AI 1.0.5&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; 10 improvements with 8 bug fixes and 2 other enhancements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Improvements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced stability with 8 bug fixes addressing vector store and streaming issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v1.0.5&quot;&gt;View complete release notes ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;spring-ai-114&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#spring-ai-114&quot; aria-label=&quot;spring ai 114 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Spring AI 1.1.4&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; 13 improvements with 1 new feature, 11 bug fixes, and 1 other enhancement&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Improvements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added dynamic structured output control capability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced stability with 11 bug fixes across vector stores, model integrations, and caching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v1.1.4&quot;&gt;View complete release notes ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;spring-ai-200-m4&quot; style=&quot;position:relative;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#spring-ai-200-m4&quot; aria-label=&quot;spring ai 200 m4 permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor before&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Spring AI 2.0.0-M4&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; 28 improvements with 2 new features, 10 bug fixes, 13 other enhancements, and 3 dependency upgrades&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;? Noteworthy:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Vertex AI model integration classes have been deprecated and will be removed in a future release. Users should plan to migrate to alternative model providers. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/pull/5676&quot;&gt;#5676&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ZhiPu AI model integration classes have been deprecated and will be removed in a future release. Users should plan to migrate to alternative model providers. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/pull/5676&quot;&gt;#5676&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The OCI GenAI model integration classes have been deprecated and will be removed in a future release. Users should plan to migrate to alternative model providers. &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/pull/5676&quot;&gt;#5676&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Improvements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enhanced Google Search integration for Gemini 3.x models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Added dynamic structured output control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stability improvements with 10 bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Updated dependencies including Google GenAI SDK 1.44.0, OpenAI SDK 4.28.0, and Anthropic SDK 2.17.0&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-ai/releases/tag/v2.0.0-M4&quot;&gt;View complete release notes ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
