&lt;p&gt;This release includes &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/releases/tag/v4.1.0-M4&quot;&gt;30 enhancements, documentation improvements, dependency upgrades, and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt;.
Primarily, it reverts Rabbit and AMQP changes made in M3 that will now be delivered in Spring Boot 4.2.
If you are upgrading from M3, you may need to revert to the previous AMQP starter POMs. It also fixes a regression in application.properties/application.yaml processing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please see the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-Boot-4.1.0-M4-Release-Notes&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; for more details and upgrade instructions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks to all those who have contributed with issue reports and pull requests.&lt;/p&gt;
